    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>One of the standard alloys of brass, containing 70% copper and 30% zinc. It has high ductility and an attractive yellow color, and is used for deep-drawn or spun articles such as lamp bases, horns, and cornets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
